@node main "CYCAS DEMO - Help - Functionlists"
@toc "help.guide/main"


  Brief overview of the functions:

            All the function lists are grouped together in
  subordination to the topic of each function. For example,
  note  that the  function lists

   "Project"  and
   "Symbol"

  contain various data functions.

  The function lists

   "Line",
   "Circle",
   "Dim",
   "Text",
   "3D" and
   "Unit"

  are  subordinated  to  the  different  types  of drawing
  elements.

  The function list

   "Edit"

  contains  the functions which can be used globally for a
  ll elements.


@endnode
